channel.title: Project Aurion - #474
channel.description:
[center][b][size=18pt]Project Aurion - #474[/size][/b] [size=14pt]Absolutely revolutionary[/size][/center] Hello Moparscape. Following Vigan20's release of a #474 server I will be attempting to construct one of the only 474 revisions that exist. Most of you might have have seen my release of Natural Born Killers which hopefully slightly upgraded the useless Delta servers which are consistently being overused. Hopefully this can boost the quality of servers enormously. This will also be released once I feel that I have done enough. [b]Client base[/b]: 474 Deob [b]Server base[/b]: Project ViX 474 [b]Update Log[/b]:
[b]Walking[/b] - 4th of July 2010 [b]Log out[/b] - 4th of July 2010 [b]Packaged the source[/b] - 4th of July 2010 [b]Running[/b] - 4th of July 2010
[b]Pictures[/b]: [i]Coming soon.[/i] - Tyler
